@631  = ~[SAFANA 1] I've been looking for... strong men like yourselves.~ [%tutu_var%SAFAN01]
@632  = ~[SAFANA 2] Nothing's worth dying for.~ [%tutu_var%SAFAN02]
@633  = ~[SAFANA 4] Mmmmm.  I keep very pleasant company.~ [%tutu_var%SAFAN04]
